FTLOS fans;
I can’t believe it’s been just over a year since the successful completion of our Kickstarter campaign. Boy how time flies when you’re working on For The Love Of Spock!
As of last week, we have officially delivered the finished film to our distributor! While there’s still a few steps left before our final release in September, it’s exciting to think that we’re finally reaching the finish line! (Whew!!)
